<BaseLayout title="About">
  <h1>About</h1>

  <p>
    I'm Andrew Rich (he/him). I live in Spokane, WA with my spouse Jen and an
    unreasonable number of cats.
  </p>

  <p>
    Engineer, Army veteran, IRONMAN triathlete, voice actor, and indie developer.
    I don't speak for my employer.
  </p>

  <p>
    By day I work in government technology. By night I build apps and automations
    under <a href="https://nightowlstudio.us" target="_blank" rel="noopener noreferrer">Night Owl Studio, LLC</a>.
  </p>

